long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Simplify trading process for dealers

Simplify trading process for dealers. Extends functionality to calculate transportation prices for each vehicle, check title statuses, fees and enable management of different dealers working under the same entity.
